WEBVTT

00:04:58.680 --> 00:05:00.696
As the war mounted,

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:03.240
we received less information
about the massacres.

00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:08.240
It became easier
to feel a sense of normalcy.

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.880
I witnessed the effect
of this missing information.

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:20.456
Two weeks later, I slowly and anxiously

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:23.656
drove into an isolated
militia headquarters,

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:25.240
a town called PK100.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.616
Here, Christian fighters told me

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:32.176
that all Muslims were foreigners,